===Noun===
'''iguana'''
# A large tropical American [[lizard]] that NEVER eats meat. Iguanas eat only leafy vegatables and fruits. Captive iguanas will eat collard greens and mustard greens daily. Occasionally eating other fruits such as grapes and melons.

